data.description: Welcome to this stunning one-story home in Lakes at Northpointe. With 4 bedrooms and 2 baths, this spacious and inviting home is sure to impress. Step inside, and you'll be greeted by an open and bright living space, featuring tasteful upgrades throughout. The kitchen is a chef's delight and the primary suite is a tranquil retreat, complete with a luxurious en-suite bath featuring a soaking tub and separate shower. The secondary bedrooms are generously sized with bedroom 4 making for a perfect bonus room/flex space. Outside, the backyard is a private oasis, with a spacious patio area perfect for entertaining or relaxation. This beautiful home also includes a two-car garage and is zoned to Tomball ISD, conveniently located near schools, parks, and shopping centers with convenient access to Hwy 249, 99 and Beltway 8. Call today to schedule your showing!
